{"tid":388101,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"行動不便老父買錯熱飲 18歲逆子擸拐杖打父母","createTime":"2017-09-05T08:03:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-05T08:23:33.000Z","uid":8478,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e58266ece0737761ff3cf11565ef9f1b6508034c","tid":388101,"uid":8478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T08:03:00.000Z","msg":"沙田發生逆子打父母事件。昨晚11時許，水泉澳邨嶺泉樓一名18歲姓楊青年，叫83歲行動不便的老父替他落街買飯盒及凍飲。詎料老父回家後，青年發現父親買錯熱飲，他情緒激動，喝罵老父及母親(54歲)，並取起父親的拐杖襲擊兩老，兩老負傷逃至樓下大堂向保安員求助，由保安代為報案。<br />\n<br />\n警員接報到場，將姓楊青年拘捕，涉嫌襲擊致造成實際身體傷害。而受傷的兩老則由救護車送院治理。據悉，涉案的楊男於2016年時，曾涉嫌打傷母親。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20170904/57168924\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20170904%2F57168924&d=AA1KCNrHYCdSNSZN7dlTNgRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=f5c3e494\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20170904%2F57168924&h=55319728\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20170904/57168924</a><br />\n留名睇潮文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0d6f69f1d1b9346c41604cdd81b9d84a866934a","tid":388101,"uid":8478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T08:06:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9143e49ce43e78f5eb5db082c62a90b529b9173","tid":388101,"uid":4709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T08:07:37.000Z","msg":"🥖"},{"pid":"accb1d9f9d26a1fe06f83c5e5fb65f815193a145","tid":388101,"uid":3203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T08:08:24.000Z","msg":"唔用法包打？"},{"pid":"3e01ec535d0411b6c7554962b662e51fb8404d4a","tid":388101,"uid":72929,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T08:11:01.000Z","msg":"18歲仔83歲老豆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />